Building
--------

Before building, you will need to have the Qt4 library installed
on your system (http://www.trolltech.com/).

Build:
$ qmake # or qmake-qt4
$ make  # or mingw32-make or nmake or other
Test it:
$ bin/zoclock
Install:
$ sudo cp bin/zoclock /usr/local/bin/zoclock

Enjoy!
